{"tid":2321851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫苗系列：大陸孩童跨境注射 港媽憂慮一針難求","createTime":"2020-12-12T00:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T06:58:04.000Z","uid":179775,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b7772f8e01832eae6500ae11247d193da21f1e","tid":2321851,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:14:35.000Z","msg":"根據公開資料，2011至2016年間，香港衛生署轄下母嬰健康院的兒童健康服務就診人次中，非符合資格的就診人數（藍線）連年攀升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/features/hottopic/vaccineseries/vaccine-06292016081308.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Ffeatures%2Fhottopic%2Fvaccineseries%2Fvaccine-06292016081308.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=393ef5ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/features/hottopic/vaccineseries/vaccine-06292016081308.html</a><br />\n<br />\n記者問：你有沒有認識朋友親戚到香港打（疫苗）？<br />\n<br />\n蔡仕芹：有，有，有。我居住附近，大家在閒談時說有朋友在香港接種疫苗，從一個報道及新聞，大陸都是很多人都到香港打疫苗。我不敢（再帶女兒打針了）要打都來香港打， 近期出現疫苗事件，很多（家長）亦不敢（帶小朋友）打疫苗，怕假疫苗會注射到自己小朋友身上。<br />\n<br />\n好似胡太的情況，令香港家長擔心各種疫苗在求過於供之下，影響自己子女的權益。<br />\n<br />\n在同一健康院內，香港家長徐太就與胡太不一樣的心情，她向本台表示，雖然母嬰健康院對大陸來港的嬰兒設定疫苗配額，但大陸愈來愈多家長帶子女來香港打針，擔心連私家診所也被攻陷，影響本地兒童的服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1102270486631685/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1102270486631685%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=9feaedc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1102270486631685/</a><br />\n2019年51黃金週專程來港打針"},{"pid":"5d18ee0cf1e003aeab852a110338e96d0f71477f","tid":2321851,"uid":89752,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"咪俾佢地打law<br />\n唔好同我講你想打第一輪"},{"pid":"da4846c8805040fd2fb516f12f181a6606593d62","tid":2321851,"uid":103654,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"之前死都唔限班支那嚟搶疫苗搶奶粉，依家同你講要你打咗先。盲既都知批針有問題，都唔撚駛政治化，常識諗都諗到。"},{"pid":"81c5af4d18a5f8c07d2546ca904a1583f2f523de","tid":2321851,"uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"大陸冇疫苗打咩？同維尼反映下阿嘛"},{"pid":"69dd7ab2fc7c26c4291b94bf52110f951f49fc87","tid":2321851,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T00:58:02.000Z","msg":"不如訪問下黃絲"},{"pid":"cadafb8831ca969b40328785dd8ef875784db423","tid":2321851,"uid":49685,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"無任歡迎，不過一定要收錢，最好支那貨留晒畀支那人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真香港人打真美國疫苗，唔打支那疫苗，亦都唔得支那製嘅復星輝瑞疫苗，只打美國製嘅輝瑞疫苗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f646828f35fead22978be4e023bb134b28d145","tid":2321851,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"佢地跟國內普通疫苗都信唔過<br />\n點叫香港人信"},{"pid":"1090814b7df8a26a20408613c5ce3af0fabfbd07","tid":2321851,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35f646828f35fead22978be4e023bb134b28d145","tid":2321851,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"佢地跟國內普通疫苗都信唔過<br />\n點叫香港人信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:08:44.000Z","msg":"佢地驚連支那制疫苗都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4f6f4eb5ad89963c20129df0f3098962eee9d9","tid":2321851,"uid":26773,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35f646828f35fead22978be4e023bb134b28d145","tid":2321851,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"佢地跟國內普通疫苗都信唔過<br />\n點叫香港人信"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"國內有咩信得過 ？"},{"pid":"f786892576ca8fe0c8830e6ac6706bdf5c7468dd","tid":2321851,"uid":29704,"like"