 />\n連流感針都要落香港打"},{"pid":"42a6f4e3ec0d3dc374a13ec52b506fb3b6d9ed0e","tid":2321851,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"當連母嬰健康院個d麻疹呀<br />\n最普通最普通既針<br />\n佢地都信唔過中國<br />\n<br />\n點叫香港人信新開發既"},{"pid":"01ff528f052159d2719be86139a184376f3fc43f","tid":2321851,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f646828f35fead22978be4e023bb134b28d145","tid":2321851,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"佢地跟國內普通疫苗都信唔過<br />\n點叫香港人信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"香港喺打外國貨喇喇聲落嚟打哂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人唔使打㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d724a4fe8793de3ae29f1947967c8ef08c588c","tid":2321851,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"肺炎疫苗都應該由支那童打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522b6b2751b4d0b90be7408c621573c11b48ac92","tid":2321851,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:59:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55e7c76bc2ed2bd3d36e68304d2953bb6538e207","tid":2321851,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cadafb8831ca969b40328785dd8ef875784db423","tid":2321851,"uid":49685,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"無任歡迎，不過一定要收錢，最好支那貨留晒畀支那人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真香港人打真美國疫苗，唔打支那疫苗，亦都唔得支那製嘅復星輝瑞疫苗，只打美國製嘅輝瑞疫苗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"你話事？"},{"pid":"3fc0686f1a5623cf1879e69141885ebd752b7464","tid":232